{"tid":2263860,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"兩人被指今年5月中連儂牆襲擊「休班」警一度還柙 今日控方宣布撤控","createTime":"2020-10-30T07:59:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T11:47:19.000Z","uid":240362,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"4c34fd38ad9d9910ea1f0cb60e7ee5fe967d6bf4","tid":2263860,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T07:59:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10828\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F10828&d=L3LYojiCq%2FWCCnzMgLa5KPZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=ad9f3ea4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10828</a><br />\n#九龍城裁判法院第一庭<br />\n#鄭念慈裁判官 #20200515黃大仙 #提堂 <br />\n<br />\nD1林（27）🛑曾經還押3天<br />\nD2劉（22）🛑曾經還押3天<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n對他人身體加以嚴重傷害罪（疑私了休班警）<br />\n<br />\n案情：2020年5月15日在黃大仙龍蟠苑外一條行人天橋，與其他不知名人士非法及惡意對一名休班警員A的身體加以嚴重傷害<br />\n<br />\n控方已索取法律意見<br />\n<br />\n🎉🎉撤控🎉🎉<br />\n<br />\n💛D1可以直接離開💛<br />\n<br />\nD2有訟費申請，根據刑事索訟條例第3條1A，由於D2有配合案件調查，保持緘密，沒做任何事，所以申請。<br />\n<br />\n控方反對，亦提及528張宣傳單張裏，控方檢驗到D2指模，自招嫌疑，共53個手指印及手掌印。<br />\n宣傳單亦是事件發生的原因，即是D2當時一定是在現場，閉路電視亦檢視到有人與D1一同前往現場，D1亦交了D2名字出來。<br />\n當時有6人襲擊PW1，只是認人手續認不到D2。<br />\n<br />\n辯方指就算有指模亦不代表被告一定在現場，亦表示認人手續認不到D2沒太大關係<br />\n<br />\n（法庭正在考慮，稍後再更新）"},{"pid":"d50ad30e5ac0b783b6592690f516e150eda66d76","tid":2263860,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T07:59:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"687e7c3ef33c3944977c115d64781c4bae4d3e1b","tid":2263860,"uid":231583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T08:00:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6cd24b301099ae9dc02c60b791e2b03a64ff0c22","tid":2263860,"uid":105691,"like":1,"dislike":20,"score":-19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T08:01:46.000Z","msg":"我地只要食多d黃店 打Twitter 戰線<br />\n就可以努力返工 安坐家中光復到香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算手足上庭我地都有旁聽師<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以手足方面唔需要擔心 佢地唔孤獨<br />\n我建議香港人課金比david 幫我地抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n繼續推12手足po推到佢地見到為止就贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我好撚鍾意香港 <br />\n今生只嫁前線巴 <br />\n博盡無悔<br />\n不自由 毋寧死"},{"pid":"64c62a71a95ec7d8ccbc55c4257bb4131453eb77","tid":2263860,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T08:02:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36afc7e942e1399fe81259ca152e6bab67548bfa","tid":2263860,"uid":323740,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T08:03:31.000Z","msg":"食返三日黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcc73df7b1800e9aa2ab6fd5d0abd312826ae490","tid":2263860,"uid":243677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T08:03:34.000Z","msg":"平安就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8305457eb341ab37e47c5890d3da455b9dd6cbfd","tid":2263860,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"687e7c3ef33c3944977c115d64781c4bae4d3e1b","tid":2263860,"uid":231583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"reply